						<summary>

						<p>Pillar [No. 9] dugout from the main street in the village.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragmentary and damaged record seems to refer to a gift (details lost) for offerings probably to a temple.</p>						

						<p>It is in characters of the 12th century A.D.</p>						

